[![Rust](https://img.shields.io/badge/built%20with-Rust-red)](https://www.rust-lang.org/)
[![Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/version-3.2-blue)](https://github.com/andreudumitro-eng/accum-core)

## 🌟 Key Features

### 🔥 **Fair Proof-of-Contribution (F-PoC)**
- **60% Mining Shares** — Proof-of-work contributions
- **20% Loyalty Factor** — Rewards long-term participants
- **20% Bonded Stake** — Minimum 1 ACM bond with slashing

### ⚡ **ASIC Resistant**
- **Argon2id** with 256MB memory
- CPU-friendly mining design
- 2 iterations, 4 parallelism

### 🌐 **Built-in P2P Network**
- libp2p-based networking
- Automatic peer discovery
- Share propagation

### 💾 **Persistent Storage**
- RocksDB backend
- Efficient block storage
- Fast synchronization

### ⛏️ **Integrated Miner**
- Solo mining ready
- Real-time difficulty adjustment
- Automatic block submission

## 📋 Technical Specifications

| Parameter | Value |
|-----------|-------|
| Block Time | 60 seconds |
| Block Reward | 500,000 LYT (0.05 ACM) |
| Epoch Reward | 720,000,000 LYT (72 ACM) |
| Epoch Length | 1,440 blocks |
| Max Supply | 150,000,000 ACM |
| Minimum Bond | 1 ACM |
| Bond Lockup | 20,160 blocks (~14 days) |
| Difficulty Adjustment | Every 120 blocks (±25% max) |

## 🚀 Quick Start

### Prerequisites
- Rust 1.70+ (install via [rustup](https://rustup.rs/))

### Installation

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/andreudumitro-eng/accum-core
cd accum-core

# Build and run
cargo build --release
cargo run --release
